node.text:
This frisky Rooster knows how to party.

CHICK MAGNET
• 2 oz Rooster Rojo Añejo Tequila with smoked Pineapple @rooster.rojo
• 1 oz Grapefruit Liqueur
• 1 oz Ginger Liqueur
• 1 oz Lemon Juice
• Few drops of Saline
• Torched Absinthe Rinse
Garnish: Fresh Pineapple Wheel and Tajin

Video and Music: @BarMaxExtra @BarMaxLA

.
